          <actionDate>2018-04-27</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Review Every Act Diligently In Total Resolution or the READ IT Resolution</b></p> <p>Amends Rule XXI (Restrictions on Certain Bills) of the Rules of the House of Representatives to prohibit the consideration of a bill, joint resolution, resolution, or conference report unless its text has been publicly available in electronic form for a number of minutes equal to two times the number of its pages.</p>]]></text>
